
chrome ext window resizer:
 ui
  list of presets
  save as
 save
  save position all windows with their tabs (window.screenX, screenY)
  save all open tabs
  save all size of windows(window.outerHeight, window.innerHeight)
  save up to three presets

 load
  set position on all windows (window.moveTo)
  load all saved tabs 
    window.open("http://myurl.domain", "myWindowName", "resizable");
  set size of all windows (window.resizeTo)
  
additional screens causing problems?
